==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Adhesiveness
<hw>Ad*he"sive*ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The quality of
sticking or adhering; stickiness; tenacity of union.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Phren.)</fld> <def>Propensity to form and maintain
attachments to persons, and to promote social intercourse.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Adhibit</ent>⟦br⟧
